{"title":"java二进制转换","date":"2019-01-20T17:52:00.000Z","link":"post/300","categories":["Java"],"updated":"2019-04-27T12:16:14.483Z","content":"<h3 id=\"十转二进制\">十转二进制<a href=\"post/300#十转二进制\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">String binaryStr = java.lang.Integer.toBinaryString(data);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"二进制转十进制\">二进制转十进制<a href=\"post/300#二进制转十进制\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">String a = <span class=\"string\">\"0100\"</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> d = Integer.parseInt(a, <span class=\"number\">2</span>); <span class=\"comment\">// 2进制</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> o = Integer.parseInt(a, <span class=\"number\">8</span>); <span class=\"comment\">// 8进制</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">System.out.println(d);</span><br><span class=\"line\">System.out.println(o);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"10进制变为3进制（n进制）字符串\">10进制变为3进制（n进制）字符串<a href=\"post/300#10进制变为3进制（n进制）字符串\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">String threeForm = Integer.toString(<span class=\"number\">5</span>, <span class=\"number\">3</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"后台接受post请求参数乱码问题","link":"post/303"},"next":{"title":"List集合内的元素进行顺序、倒序、随机排序","link":"post/299"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/300/"}